cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Cogniflow in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "Cogniflow: a bi-temporal RAG platform with system-time replay"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Madishetti
    given-names: Nagendhra
repository-code: "https://github.com/Open-Cognition-Labs/cogniflow"
license: Apache-2.0
abstract: >-
  Cogniflow stores every fact on two independent time axes (event time and system time),
  serving cited, temporally-correct answers and replaying past belief states without
  leaking later corrections into the past (the un-knowing invariant, enforced in CI).
keywords:
  - retrieval-augmented-generation
  - bitemporal
  - temporal-knowledge-graph
  - audit
  - provenance
